an" target="_blank">Taliban</a> <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/September_11_attacks" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/September_11_attacks" target="_blank">attack</a> on a <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/School" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/School" target="_blank">school</a> in <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peshawar" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peshawar" target="_blank">Peshawar</a> PakistanAnd just one <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Month" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Month" target="_blank">month</a> ago 89 <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boy" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boy" target="_blank">boys</a> were abducted as they <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/SAT" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/SAT" target="_blank">sat</a> an <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eleven_plus_exam" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eleven_plus_exam" target="_blank">exam</a> in their <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Sudan" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Sudan" target="_blank">South Sudan</a> <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/School" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/School" target="_blank">school</a> They were allegedly <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Force" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Force" target="_blank">forced</a> to become <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Military_use_of_children" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Military_use_of_children" target="_blank">child soldiers</a> joining an estimated 12000 othersUnited <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nation" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nation" target="_blank">Nations</a> <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diplomatic_rank" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diplomatic_rank" target="_blank">Special Envoy</a> for <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Globalization" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Globalization" target="_blank">Global</a> <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Education" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ed